        <updateDate>2009-04-14T20:16:55Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Helping Families Afford to Work Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code relating to the dependent care tax credit to: (1) increase from $15,000 to $20,000 the income threshold at which the rate of such credit is reduced; (2) increase the rate of such credit from 35 to 50%; (3) increase the maximum dollar amount of such credit; and (4) make such credit refundable. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
